{"tid":1857160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔派口罩 每人派8個 中午12時半開始派籌 名額1100個 要出示香港身分證或長者卡","createTime":"2020-02-02T05:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T05:47:53.000Z","uid":285559,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2295351023b5368ea375a37c7c2eeeea7b41117b","tid":1857160,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情下，市民四出購買口罩。位於大埔富善邨的三水同鄉會禤景榮學校今日（2日）在校派口罩，中午12時半開始派籌，名額1100個，下午2時半向每名持籌者派8個口罩。校方稱，派發行動是香港人優先，要出示香港身分證或長者卡，不會收集任何個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n校方表示，眼見疫情蔓延，香港口罩嚴重缺貨，校監兼東瀛遊執行董事禤國全蒐羅了1.8萬個口罩，並捐贈該批口罩予學校，派發予大埔區居民，希望與市民共同抗疫，解決燃眉之急；又稱由於口罩數量有限，不希望太早公布，令市民通宵輪候，特意速戰速決，望市民諒解。<br />\n<br />\n校方同時會將1200個口罩，透過機構捐給獨居長者及傷健人士；並將數千個口罩給予區內幼稚園及學校。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200202/s00001/1580616175288/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e4%b8%89%e6%b0%b4%e5%90%8c%e9%84%89%e6%9c%83%e7%a6%a4%e6%99%af%e6%a6%ae%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1%e4%bb%8a%e6%b4%be%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e5%90%8d%e9%a1%8d1100%e5%80%8b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200202%2Fs00001%2F1580616175288%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%2590%258c%25e9%2584%2589%25e6%259c%2583%25e7%25a6%25a4%25e6%2599%25af%25e6%25a6%25ae%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e4%25bb%258a%25e6%25b4%25be%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e5%2590%258d%25e9%25a1%258d1100%25e5%2580%258b&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9GAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=fc761084\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200202%2Fs00001%2F1580616175288%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%2590%258c%25e9%2584%2589%25e6%259c%2583%25e7%25a6%25a4%25e6%2599%25af%25e6%25a6%25ae%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e4%25bb%258a%25e6%25b4%25be%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9-%25e5%2590%258d%25e9%25a1%258d1100%25e5%2580%258b&h=7a6fa69f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200202/s00001/1580616175288/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e4%b8%89%e6%b0%b4%e5%90%8c%e9%84%89%e6%9c%83%e7%a6%a4%e6%99%af%e6%a6%ae%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1%e4%bb%8a%e6%b4%be%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9-%e5%90%8d%e9%a1%8d1100%e5%80%8b</a>"},{"pid":"9ac04559cd693867731a9b5829ccf43a4e9d6347","tid":1857160,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"823d3e5b50108bdd22308b311f478fb086d1ceeb","tid":1857160,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:21:49.000Z","msg":"同意派比傷殘人士<br />\n但係點解要派比廢老?"},{"pid":"527f1187013565e4ac7018d2c2516e29bf605dda","tid":1857160,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"政府：派口罩不可行，將不斷聯絡口罩供應商。"},{"pid":"19ba28d04a7c93af2531a8aa43a92029c85fcca7","tid":1857160,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"1340已派完籌"}]}